stimulus:
Hello!

You will be taking part in a stroop experiment. You will see one the following words displayed:

  • 'red'
  • 'blue'
  • 'orange'
  • 'green'

And the displayed word will be colored in one of the four colors. Not necessarily in the same color as shown above


Press any key to continue.

Your role will be to press the 'F' key when the word corresponds to the actual color,
or press the 'J' key when the word and color is mismatched.

Press any key to continue.
